Improve Licensing ROI

Reduce overhead and focus on income-producing activities that make your license pay for itself.

High-Return Activities

  • Builder & new-home sales center introductions
  • Relocation and out-of-area referrals
  • Past-client check-ins that convert to listings/buys via partners
  • Seasonal / life-event outreach (marriage, new baby, downsizing)

Sample Math (Illustrative)

ScenarioExample
Referral side commission$9,000
Referral fee (e.g., 25%)$2,250
Net to you (before taxes)$2,250
Replace example amounts with your market numbers. The goal: keep costs low and referral volume steady.

Tools

  • ARAD referral templates (DocuSign)
  • Status updates through closing
  • Clear payout statements
